edge: Emilia Jones portrays the character of Ruby Rossi in the movie.
In the movie, Ruby Rossi interacts with Bernardo 'Mr. V' Villalobos, played by Eugenio Derbez.
Ruby Rossi is the daughter of Frank Rossi portrayed by Troy Kotsur in the movie.
Ruby Rossi has a romantic interest in Miles, portrayed by Ferdia Walsh-Peelo in the movie.
In the movie, Frank Rossi is married to Jackie Rossi played by Marlee Matlin.
Ruby Rossi and Leo Rossi, portrayed by Daniel Durant, are siblings in the movie.
In the movie, Amy Forsyth plays the role of Ruby's best friend Gertie.
Ruby Rossi interacts with Tanya, portrayed by Sarah Clarke in the movie.
In the movie, Brady is portrayed by Kevin Chapman.
In the movie, Tony Salgado is played by John Fiore.
In the movie, Joanne Biles is portrayed by Rebecca Gibel.
